Help MysticView:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Mystics and sorcerers work well together, since their magic functions in a 
similar fashion.  They sometimes find themselves at odds with those who 
worship or revere the deities, such as clerics, knights, and wizards of high
sorcery.  
